      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and dice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Peel and chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic </strong>finely</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>Knorr</strong> <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>in 700ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
